title: install
extract: Definition of install. transitive verb. 1a : to place in an office or dignity by seating in a stall or official seat. b : to induct into an office, rank, or order installed the new president.
extract_html: Definition of install. transitive verb. 1a : to place in an office or dignity by seating in a stall or official seat. b : to induct into an office, rank, or order installed the new president.
